# Write a program to print given number is perfect or not?

n=int(input())
i=1
s=0
while(i<n):
    if(n%i==0):
        s=s+i
    i=i+1
if(s==n):
      print("Perfect number")
else:
      print("Not a perfect number")

******OUTPUT-1**********
6
Perfect number

*******OUTPUT-2*********
7
Not a perfect number
